goal: Create a reminder for June 1st to review crossing guard performance.

steps: Click the Create button to start creating a new reminder
Select 'Task' from the create menu to continue creating a reminder for June 1st.
Fill in the title of the reminder with 'Review crossing guard performance'.
Set the start date of the reminder to 'June 1, 2025' using the date picker.
Click the Save button to save the reminder
